r-rOATA3YE3xI-b4gI-_iYag">Phạm Thận Duật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Nhi%E1%BB%87t-th%E1%BB%9Di-t%C3%A1c/poem-HPcWDHbQ0PPoQzaZzkoq3Q">Nhiệt thời tác - 爇時作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%A1c-V%C4%83n-Qu%C3%A2n/O%C3%A1n-lang-thi/poem-Wfh32XMnl_XYSnuAyPiM6g">Oán lang thi - 怨郎詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%A1c-V%C4%83n-Qu%C3%A2n/author-kBdgVic3JnKgw1IGHv_v2g">Trác Văn Quân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/Tam-t%E1%BB%B1-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-lnZAP3HTCiQ-iU-E5n8DCQ">Tam tự thi kỳ 5 - 三字詩其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-ki%E1%BB%81u-ti%C3%AAn-Hoa-%C4%91%C4%83ng-t%C3%BAng-b%C3%A1c/poem-OZLDa6CyeAwV9Jk61r2ntg">Thước kiều tiên - Hoa đăng túng bác - 鵲橋仙－華燈縱博</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br></div>	</div>
